<div class="blogpost-content">
<p>In August, the <a href="/blog:new-bootstrap-website-template">Standard Template</a> was officially released and has since then seen some success. While a very good start for general purpose sites, it is now time to start unveiling task-specific applications, starting with&#8230;</p>
